{"tid":227045,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五一3天假有49萬內地人入境，攻陷香港郊野公園","createTime":"2017-05-03T01:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T01:05:13.000Z","uid":99205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20f703362ee734d34eef3e7132898cb44dc848d4","tid":227045,"uid":99205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:03:31.000Z","msg":"見無咩人講<br />\n香港人遲下又要幫手執手尾執垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170501/large/01la1p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170501%2Flarge%2F01la1p2.jpg&h=a49d1f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170501/20007260\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170501%2F20007260&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyuPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=a2db4781\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170501%2F20007260&h=163a3122\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170501/20007260</a><br />\n<br />\n黃金周假期開始，離島出現「$0住宿」內地團！記者發現來自湖北武漢的45名內地遊客，透過旅遊網站自組香港露營體驗團，他們前晚佔據了景色怡人的長洲東灣泳灘非法紮營，20多個帳幕在沙灘上一字排開，蔚為奇觀；各人度宿一宵後，至昨日再移師到大嶼山貝澳營地繼續，3日2夜行程零住宿開支，有團友稱曾在旺角購物受氣，所以「寧看風景也不去購物」。事件除帶出內地自組旅行團欠監管，也令人關注香港傳統景點對內地客漸失吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170501/photo/bkn-20170501180208761-0501_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170501224221\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170501%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170501180208761-0501_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170501224221&h=c0924629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170501/photo/bkn-20170501180208761-0501_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170501224221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170501%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170501180208761-0501_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170501224221&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyuPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=5162b911\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170501/photo/bkn-20170501180208761-0501_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170501224221</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「零購物」</span></strong></span>內地生態團假期攻港，2日1夜「千元之旅」，揭本港旅遊業旺丁不旺財之謎！本港郊野營地和沙灘，近日逼爆來自內地的「露營團」，五顏六色的「營帳陣」佔據沙灘和營地，除長洲、大嶼山外，有本港露營客今日發現，交通不便的西貢鹹田灣營地，亦被內地露營團進駐，大嘆去郊外都要同人逼。據該類主打享受香港「陽光與海灘」的活動行程顯示，幾乎無時間入市區購物，每人付千元港幣「只睇風景」，估計五一假期有50個「露營團」攻港，但本港<span style=\"color: red;\">零售業沾不了光，旅遊業界亦「無肉食」</span>。"},{"pid":"de36f9412f678f8d0aa3e2c7a168645a675c5dce","tid":227045,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:04:39.000Z","msg":"香港商界班PK咪再儲多借口啦<br />\n<br />\n人地自由行其實來好多<br />\n<br />\n係醒左唔再俾你地搵笨柒炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c79c24539d84e9ecd073009af3a809c09159d4","tid":227045,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:04:42.000Z","msg":"香港做生意包賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868f0589a119622d1ba8c224dffa19ad97cb9f7a","tid":227045,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:05:13.000Z","msg":"商戶又要叫春"}]}